POE-Component-CSS-Minifier

The module is a non-blocking wrapper around L<CSS::Minifier>, which provides interface to
strip useless spaces from CSS code. The wrapper also provides additional functionality to
fetch CSS from URI.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc POE::Component::CSS::Minifier

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=POE-Component-CSS-Minifier

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/POE-Component-CSS-Minifier

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/POE-Component-CSS-Minifier

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/POE-Component-CSS-Minifier


